snippet.title: Suroi v0.19.0 Trailer #1 - High-Caliber Negotiations
snippet.description:
Suroi v0.19.0 is officially out! Enjoy playing with the new L115A1, RSh-12, and DEagle in our first multi-story building, the headquarters!
